											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[AL] custom needed, , [AMN][GUS-254172] Astarion's right hand shot up quickly, grabbing the Player's neck., Locking eyes with the Player, he starts to squeeze their neck, slowly choking them ., , Player squirms a bit, gasping for breath. They're enjoying it., , Astarion then releases Player's neck, leaning over to bare his fangs and bite into Player's neck., , After a while, he stops and raises his head., , (Note: Astarion is still on top of Player, his body shifted slightly to the side (Player's right) so that he has room to take Player's neck and do all that bloodsucking stuff)" />
										</node>
