											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[AL] Custom animations will be needed., , [AMN][GUS254172] Both Astarion and Player are naked., Player stands at the foot of the bed. They look slightly to their left as Astarion approaches them from behind., He kisses the Player on the left side of their neck...then roughly pushes Player down onto the bed. Player is now bent over at the edge of the bed. Sex begins., , (Note: While the sex isn't super explicit, it's important to show suggestions of movements...such as thrusting, action/reactions of ecstasy, etc.)" />
										</node>
